  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Get on board with Inghams this April as the presenter of the BBC’s Ski Sunday and ex professional snowboarder <strong>Ed Leigh</strong> is going to be boarding with Inghams’ guests from 09.04.16 in the high-end resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a0f5a0d90fe3493faa137de4bb419db4}" title="Verbier">Verbier,</a> <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>. Ed knows Verbier inside out and is ready to share this knowledge with some lucky Inghams guests.</p>
<p><br />Verbier is renowned for its off-piste riding, deep powder, extensive mogul fields, has three snow parks and is a unique resort. It’s also a hub of parties and après ski with a lively atmosphere on and off the slopes. The ski area is extensive, modern and varied with quick and efficient resort infrastructure. The 4 diamond Xtra Chalet Hotel de Verbier boasts an excellent in location in resort on the Place Central which is aptly named by all accounts.</p>
<p><br />Inghams is offering short ski breaks, 4 nights, chalet catering at the 4.5 diamond <a data-udi="umb://document/eb091d6f78994051880c5f1e85e059bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/eb091d6f78994051880c5f1e85e059bb}" title="Xtra Chalet de Verbier">Xtra Chalet Hotel de Verbier</a>, Switzerland from £599 per person. Price includes return flights from Gatwick or Manchester to Geneva, resort transfers, chalet catering (breakfast, afternoon tea and a 5 course evening meal each night), two half days riding with Ed Leigh and an end of the week party with prizes. For more information or to book email <a href="mailto:ridewithed@inghams.co.uk">ridewithed@inghams.co.uk</a> or call 01483 791 114. <br /><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/ridewithed">www.inghams.co.uk/ridewithed</a></p>
<p><strong>For press enquiries or a copy of the brochure please contact</strong><br />PR Executive, Rachel Gaston, Inghams on 01483 79 10 45 / <a href="mailto:rachel.gaston@inghams.co.uk">rachel.gaston@inghams.co.uk</a></p>
<p>Senior PR Account Manager, Daniela Resenterra, 020 7593 1771/<a href="mailto:danielaR@hillsbalfour.com">danielaR@hillsbalfour.com</a></p>
<p>Senior PR Account Executive, Josie Self on 0207 593 1758/ <a href="mailto:JosieS@hillsbalfour.com">JosieS@hillsbalfour.com</a></p>]]></bodyText>
